What you need to know:

Dolberg struck in each half at the Johan Cruyff Arena in Amsterdam to put the Danes beyond Wales' reach before late goals from Joakim Maehle and Martin Braithwaite capped an impressive victoryIn the last eight Kasper Hjulmand's side will face either the Netherlands or the Czech Republic in Baku on July 3Carried by a wave of emotion, Danish dreams are still intact in a tournament that began in such traumatic circumstances for them with Eriksen's collapse in their opening match